Prequisites:-

1.A linux system
2.MySQL
3.Python 2.7.10 or above
4.nltk library in python
5.punkt module in nltk


Steps to Run:-

1.Run script deploy.sh

	sh deploy.sh

  This basically creates a new user in MySQL and creates a database in MySQL

2.You should keep the corpus in a different directory

3.Run python main.py in terminal 

  If you are running for the first time.You will have to initialise the database.
  For that you need to know the complete path of the directory where the corpus is stored.
  
Note:-
1.When running the program you will be prompted if you want to initialise the database
2.The creation of the database is logged in the log file 'LOG_IR_A1.log'
